    "body": "Finally found the settings, I knew it's somewhere.\n\ngo to matrix project -> Configure -> Advanced Project Options -> Restrict where this project can be run -> set to label \"linux\".\n\nThat should only affect where the parent job will be run, the logic to pick workers for child runs should stay the same.\n"
